This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for resolving abstract anaphora, which is a subfield of computational linguistics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses LSTM-Siamese Net, which is a deep learning architecture commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper generates artificial data, which is a common technique in neural network training (cs.NE). Finally, the paper mentions the use of deeper features, which could involve computer vision techniques (cs.CV).
